The '''Grand Rim Promenade''' was a large open market in the [[Canyonade]] on [[Cejansij]]. It was located two-thirds of the way up the eastern slope, was thirty [[Meter/Legends|meters]] wide, and ran all ten [[Kilometer/Legends|kilometers]] of the [[canyon]].<ref name="Specter of the Past">''[[Specter of the Past]]''</ref>

